      "query": "What is the correct SKF metric radial shaft seal designation for a 55mm shaft, 72mm housing bore, and 8mm width utilizing the standard NBR lip material? Please provide the specific HMSA10 SKU so we can avoid ordering the fluoro rubber version by mistake.",
